dder/2000/12/25/krtbn/0000-0034-HP-ELECTRIC

PSEG, MARUBENI BUY SITHE'S STAKE IN TUNISIAN POWER PLANT
Public Service Enterprise Group Inc. and Marubeni Corp have bought Sithe's 
interest in a 471-megawatt power plant under development in Rades, Tunisia, 
PSEG said Tuesday.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2000/
12/26/eng-djn/eng-djn_144036_87_3467169469222

CHINA TO BUILD MORE NATURAL GAS POWER PLANTS
China will build a number of power projects fueled with natural gas in the 
2001-2005 period, according to the State Power Corporation.
